v 0.2.0 - beta5
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Kipi-plugins NEW FEATURES:

RemoveRedEyes  : Added an option to preview the correction of the currently selected image.

Kipi-plugins BUG FIXING from B.K.O (http://bugs.kde.org):

001 ==> 169637 : MetadataEdit       : EXIF Data Editing Error.
002 ==> 174954 : HTMLExport         : Support for remote urls.
003 ==> 176640 : MetadataEdit       : Wrong reference to website.
004 ==> 176749 : TimeAdjust         : Incorrect time/date setting with digiKam.
005 ==> 165370 : GPSSync            : crash when saving geocoordinates.
006 ==> 165486 : GPSSync            : Next and Previous photo button for editing geolocalization coordinates.
007 ==> 175296 : GPSSync            : Geolocalization a handy gui to manage all about geotagging.
008 ==> 152520 : MetadataEdit       : Unified entry of metadata.
009 ==> 135320 : Calendar           : Calendar year do not match locale.
010 ==> 

v 0.2.0 - beta4
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Kipi-plugins NEW FEATURES:

RemoveRedEyes  : New plugin to remove red eyes in batch. Tool is based on OpenCV library.
Calendar       : Ported to QT4/KDE4.
Calendar       : Support RAW images.
AcquireImages  : Under Windows, TWAIN interface is used to scan image using flat scanner.
SlideShow      : Normal effects are back.
SlideShow      : New effect "Cubism".
SlideShow      : Added support for RAW images.
DNGConverter   : plugin is now available as a stand alone application.
SlideShow      : New effect "Mosaic"
PrintWizard    : Ported to QT4/KDE4
PrintWizard    : Added a new option to skip cropping, the image is scaled automatically.

Kipi-plugins BUG FIXING from B.K.O (http://bugs.kde.org):

001 ==> 172910 : GalleryExport      : Gallery crash (letting crash digiKam) with valid data and url.
002 ==> 161855 : GalleryExport      : Remote Gallery Sync loses password.
003 ==> 154752 : GalleryExport      : Export to Gallery2 seems to fail, but in fact works.
004 ==> 157285 : SlideShow          : digiKam advanced slideshow not working with Canon RAWs.
005 ==> 175316 : GPSSync            : digiKam crashes when trying to enter gps data.

v 0.2.0 - beta3
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Kipi-plugins NEW FEATURES:

General        : all plugins can be compiled natively under Microsoft Windows.

Kipi-plugins BUG FIXING from B.K.O (http://bugs.kde.org):

